Package org.cloudbus.foggatewaylib.core

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AsyncProvider.ProgressPublisher
    Interface used for passing the progress updates from the AsyncProvider context to the AsyncProvider.ProviderAsyncTask one and finally calling Provider.publishProgresses(long, ProgressData...).
    ExecutionManager.Holder
    Simple interface for a class that holds an ExecutionManager reference.
    InMemoryStore.BackingCollection<E extends java.lang.Comparable>
    Interface for a Collection to be used as the backing data structure for the InMemoryStore.
    Store.Observer<T extends Data>
    Simple interface for registering callbacks when a new element is added to a Store.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndroidExecutionManager
    Execution Manager with a Context property.
    AndroidProvider<T extends Data,S extends Data>
    Provider with Android-specific thread-safe methods for publishing progress and results.
    AsyncProvider<T extends Data,S extends Data>
    Abstract implementation of a Provider based on AsyncTask.
    Chooser
    This class performs a choice between different Providers that provide the same output.
    Data
    Base class for all data types managed by this library.
    DummyProvider<T extends Data>
    A simple dummy provider that copies the input to the output and publishes a progress with the given value and message.
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExecutionManager
    Orchestrator and manager of the other components (Store, Provider, Chooser, Trigger).
    FilteredTrigger<T extends Data>
    Simple implementation of a Trigger that filters data based on the request id before triggering.
    GenericData<T>
    Generic class for any type of Data.
    IndividualTrigger<T extends Data>
    Extension of a Trigger that executes the callback on every incoming data inside IndividualTrigger.onDataStored(Store, Data[]), instead of calling it just once with an array of Data.
    InMemoryStore<E extends Data,C extends InMemoryStore.BackingCollection>
    Implementation of a Store that uses a custom extension of a LinkedList, SortedLinkedList for storing the data in memory.
    InMemoryStoreTest  
    MiscTest  
    ProduceDataTrigger<T extends Data>
    Trigger implementation that calls ExecutionManager.produceData(String, long, Data...) for every new Data.
    ProgressData
    Data representing a progress update.
    Provider<T extends Data,S extends Data>
    Provides output data with given input data (if any).
    RoundRobinChooser
    Simple Chooser implementation using the Round-Robin algorithm.
    RunProviderTrigger<T extends Data>
    Trigger implementation that calls ExecutionManager.runProvider(String, long, Data...) for every new Data.
    SequentialProvider<T extends Data,S extends Data>
    AsyncProvider that uses a dedicated Executors.newSingleThreadExecutor() for scheduling its tasks.
    SortedDataList<E extends Data>
    Extension of the SortedLinkedList class that enables splicing with given id.
    SortedDataListTest  
    SortedDataListTest  
    Store<T extends Data>
    Collection of Data sorted by their id.
    ThreadPoolProvider<T extends Data,S extends Data>
    AsyncProvider that uses a dedicated Executors.newFixedThreadPool(int) for scheduling its tasks.
    TimerProvider<T extends Data,S extends Data>
    Abstract AsyncProvider that will call its @AsyncProvider.execute(long, Data[]) asynchronously, based on a configurable Timer.
    Trigger<T extends Data>
    Abstract implementation of a Store.Observer that is bound to an ExecutionManager.
    VoidData
    Same as Data but to be used when no data is required in input.
